  <a href="gb-skirk.html">Kirkcudbrightshire</a>, UK (fotw)
  <p>
  Please note that a �pectoral cross� is one of the badges of office worn by a bishop.  
  </em>
  </dd>

  <hr /><a name="stgeorgetypecross"></a>
