  <dt style="font-weight: bold">SAINT GEORGE'S CANTON</dt>
  <dd>See &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvc1.html#cantonstgeorge">canton of St. George</a>&rsquo;.
  <p>
  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d1178.gif">
